Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在耀眼的清風之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}繪畫你的笑顏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:42.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能坦白面對的瞬間
